WEBVTT

00:03:58.333 --> 00:04:01.809
He saw a heavy future

00:04:01.833 --> 00:04:07.643
of civil wrongs and Black power
outages in his palms.

00:04:07.667 --> 00:04:10.768
The last straw had come
the previous winter

00:04:10.792 --> 00:04:14.333
when they had gunned down Fred Hampton.

00:04:15.417 --> 00:04:18.434
Overwhelmed with fear

00:04:18.458 --> 00:04:20.226
and rage

00:04:20.250 --> 00:04:21.559
and grief,

00:04:21.583 --> 00:04:25.018
Uncle Freeman tried to game his future.

00:04:25.042 --> 00:04:26.976
He gripped too tight,

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:29.309
and he started playing the numbers.

00:04:29.333 --> 00:04:31.934
"Well, one of these numbers
is gonna hit, little girl.